13
00:00:41,530 --> 00:00:48,300
Lx, if you remember
the cross-product rule,

14
00:00:48,300 --> 00:00:56,760
that would be y Pz minus z Py.

15
00:00:56,760 --> 00:01:00,930
Now you can think of
this thing as a cyclic,

16
00:01:00,930 --> 00:01:10,500
like a circle when you have x
and Px, y and Py, and z and Pz.

17
00:01:10,500 --> 00:01:14,290
Things are cyclically symmetric.

18
00:01:14,290 --> 00:01:17,020
There's no real difference
between this core.

19
00:01:17,020 --> 00:01:20,370
And so you can go
