20
00:01:20,370 --> 00:01:23,330
So you say, let's go
cyclical on this index.

21
00:01:23,330 --> 00:01:28,845
Ly is equal to the next
cyclic to y in that direction

22
00:01:28,845 --> 00:01:35,550
