23
00:01:35,550 --> 00:01:46,104
And Lz is equal to
x Py minus y Px.

24
00:01:51,780 --> 00:01:57,310
And these things, I'll think
of them as the operators.

25
00:01:57,310 --> 00:02:01,740
Let's put hats to everything.

26
00:02:01,740 --> 00:02:05,430
The first thing I can
